  Please note that we cannot be held responsible for shipping delays due to holidays and/or the weather.
  If you have purchased a Bâ€™ING YOU ring please allow 2 weeks for the custom order process.
  If you have purchased our ks Mentoring  program, we will send you an additional note with the information required to secure your appointment.
<% end %>

<a href="<%= order_url(@order.number) %>" target="_blank">Order#<%= @order.number %></a> (<%= Time.now %>)

<% @order.line_items.each do |item| %>
  Product: <%= "#{item.name} (##{item.variant.sku})" %>
  Quantity: <%= item.quantity %>
  Price: <%= item.single_money.to_html %>

<% end %>
---------------------------
Subtotal: <%= @order.display_item_total.to_html %>
---------------------------

Shipping: <%= Spree::Money.new(@order.shipment_total, currency: @order.currency) %> <%= @order.shipments.map { |shipment| shipment.selected_shipping_rate.name }.join(', ') %>
<% if @order.all_adjustments.tax.exists? %>
  Tax: <%= Spree::Money.new(@order.additional_tax_total, currency: @order.currency) %> via <%= @order.all_adjustments.tax.pluck(:label).uniq.join(', ') %>
<% end %>
<% if @order.all_adjustments.promotion.eligible.exists? %>
  Promotion: <%= Spree::Money.new(@order.promo_total, currency: @order.currency) %> via <%= @order.all_adjustments.promotion.eligible.pluck(:label).uniq.join(', ') %>
<% end %>
Payment Method: <%= @order.payments.map {|payment| Spree::PaymentMethod.find_with_destroyed(payment.payment_method_id).name if payment }.uniq.join(', ') %>

---------------------------
Total: <%= @order.display_total %>
---------------------------

Customer details
---------------------

  1. Email: <a href="mailto:<%= @order.email %>" target="_blank"><%= @order.email %></a>

  2. Phone: <%= @order.bill_address.phone %>

  3. Billing address: <% bill_address = @order.bill_address %>, <%= "#{bill_address.firstname} #{bill_address.lastname}" %>, <%= bill_address.address1 %>, <%= bill_address.city %>, <%= bill_address.state.name %>, <%= bill_address.zipcode %>

  4. Shipping address: <% ship_address = @order.ship_address %>, <%= "#{ship_address.firstname} #{ship_address.lastname}" %>, <%= ship_address.address1 %>, <%= ship_address.city %>, <%= ship_address.state.name %>, <%= ship_address.zipcode %>


